comments: Brooks (MEM) briefly grasps Lillard's (POR) arm but does not affect his FOM.
Lillard (POR) places his off-arm against Brooks (MEM) and the contact is marginal as he releases and steps back.
Adams (MEM) and Nurkic (POR) mutually engage and the contact is marginal.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes contact to Little's (POR) arm that affects his ability to rebound.
Bane (MEM) makes incidental hand on ball contact with Nurkic (POR) during his shot near the rim.
Bane (MEM) disengages from Powell (POR) and the contact is marginal.
Bane (MEM) steps into Lillard's (POR) path and makes marginal body contact that does not affect his ability to make the pass.
Powell (POR) moves along with Bane (MEM) as the two players engage prior to the screen.
Powell (POR) legally contests Bane's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Adams (MEM) initiates some contact with Nance Jr. (POR) during the rebound but the contact is marginal.
Brooks (MEM) places his forearm against Lillard (POR) as he releases the pass but the contact is marginal.
Brooks (MEM) makes marginal contact to Powell's (POR) body during the pass.
The Trail Blazers fail to cross the midcourt line within 8 seconds.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Lillard (POR) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Lillard (POR) makes contact to Brooks' (MEM) body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) makes contact to  Powell's (POR) arm that affects his SBQR.
Powell (POR) makes marginal contact to Bane's (MEM) arm that does not affect his FOM.
Brooks (MEM) makes contact to Little (POR) that affects his ability to secure the rebound.
